<br>
As a noob he didn't know how much stuff was worth, but he trusted the people he traded with because they were guild members.  It's pretty pathetic when players with thousands of plat rip off low level players of the few hundred PP they manage to scrape up and even worse when it's a fellow guild member.  One of the guys that ripped him off was the guy that invited him into the guild which makes the whole thing sound like a scam.<br>
<br>
The officers refuse to do anything about it which makes me think they actually condone this sort of behavior.  Maybe they think it's funny, but it's not, it's really pathetic.<br>
<br>
If you join Noir Circle, trade and buy/sell from members at your own risk and don't expect anything from the officers if you get taken.  <br>
<br>
Also watch out trading with ANY members of this guild as there seem to be quite a few dishonest members and the Guild Officers don't seem to care.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/bdrinal28133.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dreamriderrh>DreamriderRH</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>S&M Barbie</span><br>  Posts: 81<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/02 4:50:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1703.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   more facts please</span><hr size=1> How so? why don't you tell us exactly what items were traded and for how much pp, or are you afraid that you're an idiot and think shit is worth way more than it really is? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/bdrinal28133.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ryndi>Ryndi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>THogg's Lubba</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/02 5:07:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1703.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: more facts please</span><hr size=1> Quote &quot;or are you afraid that you're an idiot and think shit is worth way more than it really is?&quot;<br>
